          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>No discussion of Ralph Lauren would be complete without mentioning the iconic Bear Collection. This season, the Bear Collection brings a playful yet sophisticated twist to golf fashion, incorporating the beloved bear motif into classic pieces. From sumptuous knitwear to accessories and polo shirts, each piece is stamped with the college cool and sporty aesthetic synonymous with Ralph Lauren. Perfect to add an idiosyncratic note to a classic closet's collection of essentials, this assortment brings under the spotlight the inimitable mix of flair and personality that only Ralph Lauren can provide.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
